paper_abstract: Wiener index was introduced by Harold Wiener in 1947. This index is the sum of distances between all vertices of a graph. The edge versions of Wiener index was introduced by Iranmanesh et al. in [18]. In this paper, the first edge Wiener index of TUC4C8(S) nanotube is computed.
paper_title: COMPUTATION OF THE FIRST EDGE-WIENER INDEX OF TUC4C8(S) NANOTUBE
